'''Obihiro Shrine''' (帯廣神社, ''Obihiro jinja'') is a [[Shinto]] shrine located in [[Obihiro, Hokkaido]]. Erected in 1910, it is dedicated to the [[kami]] Ōkuni-mitama no mikoto (大國魂神), [[Ōkuninushi]] no mikoto (大那牟遲神), and [[Sukunabikona]] no mikoto (少彦名神). Its annual festival is on September 24.
==See also== *[[List of Shinto shrines in Japan#Hokkaid.C5.8D|List of Shinto shrines in Hokkaidō]]
==External links== *[http://www.obihirojinja.jp Official website] *[https://hokkaidojinjacho.jp/帯廣神社/ Hokkaido Shinto listing]
